did.unittitle: University of Pittsburgh Archives Personal Files
did.abstract:
The University of Pittsburgh Archives Personal Files contain news clippings, press releases, photographs and other materials about University of Pittsburgh faculty, staff, administrators, students and visitors. There is at least one folder in the Information File for each of the headings listed below. The files are arranged in alphabetical order by last name and are available for public use in the Archives Service Center Reading Room.
An asterisk after a name indicates that the file includes a photographic print or negative.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation

userestrict.head: Copyright
userestrict.p: The University of Pittsburgh holds the property rights to the material in the personal files, but the copyright may still be held by the original creator/author. Researchers are therefore advised to follow the regulations set forth in the U.S. Copyright Code when publishing, quoting, or reproducing material from the information files without the consent of the creator/author or that go beyond what is allowed by fair use.
